导出数据sql语句

在读设计师
select username,name,phone from users where role_id=1 and des_status = 1

上传作品数
select id,name,username,email,designs_count from users where created_at BETWEEN "2012-04-20 00:00:00" AND "2012-05-20 23:59:59"

投票，转发，评论统计
select u.id,u.name,u.username,u.email,u.role_id,u.des_status,sum(vo.id),sum(comments.id) from users as u left outer join votes as vo on vo.user_id = u.id  left outer join comments on comments.user_id = u.id where u.created_at BETWEEN "2012-04-20 00:00:00" and "2012-05-20 23:59:59" group by u.id